<%# ──────────────────────────── HERO ──────────────────────────── %>
<div class="home-hero">
  <div class="home-hero-inner">
    <p class="heading-3" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); letter-spacing: 0.15em;">Invest. Finance. Grow.</p>
    <h1 class="heading-display" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">Linchpin Realty</h1>
    <p style="max-width: 34rem; margin: 1.5rem auto 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.75;">
      Dynamic investing and loan services to elevate your
      real estate opportunities. Real estate lending made simple.
    </p>

    <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <p style="margin-top: 2rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 0.9375rem;">
        Welcome back, <strong style="color: #fff;"><%= current_user.first_name || current_user.email %></strong>.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center;">
        <%= btn_tag "Dashboard", "#" %>
        <%= button_to "Sign Out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: "btn-filled btn-filled-ghost", style: "color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);" %>
      </div>
    <% else %>
      <div class="home-actions">
        <%= btn_tag "Get a Loan", loans_path %>
        <%= btn_tag "Become a Lender", lenders_path %>
        <%= btn_tag "Invest", invest_path %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<%#
──────────────────────────── STATS BAR ────────────────────────────
Uncomment when numbers are ready to back it up.
<div class="home-stats">
  <div class="home-stats-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="stat-value">$82M+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Lifetime Funded</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="stat-value">340+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Loans Closed</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="stat-value">4 Days</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Avg. Close Time</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="stat-value">98%</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Repayment Rate</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
%>

<%# ──────────────────────────── THREE PATHS ──────────────────────────── %>
<div class="container-wide section">
  <span class="section-label">How We Work</span>

  <div class="home-grid-3">
    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">Get a Loan</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
        Specialized hard money loans for individuals navigating the
        hurdles of traditional financing. Whether you need a bridge
        loan, rehab financing, or a fast close, we provide practical
        solutions that move at the speed of your deal.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <%= btn_tag "Apply Now", loans_path %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">Become a Lender</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
        Engage as a hard money lender and earn competitive returns
        backed by real property. We provide transparent terms,
        first-position liens, and consistent deal flow so you
        can put your capital to work with confidence.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <%= btn_tag "Learn More", lenders_path %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">Invest</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
        Real estate investment opportunities regardless of capital level.
        From individual properties to portfolio-level participation,
        we open the door to new real estate investment for those
        ready to grow.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <%= btn_tag "View Opportunities", invest_path %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── MISSION ──────────────────────────── %>
<div style="background: var(--color-smoke); border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
  <div class="container-wide section">
    <div class="home-grid-2">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label">Our Mission</span>
        <p class="heading-1">Ethical Principles.<br>Practical Solutions.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-body">
          Our mission centers on ethical principles and practical solutions,
          prioritizing transparency, integrity, and excellence in every
          interaction. Whether you are borrowing, lending, or investing,
          we structure every deal to protect all parties and deliver
          real returns.
        </p>
        <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
          Born in Queens and now operating out of Southern California,
          Linchpin Realty brings a hands-on, no-nonsense approach to
          every deal we touch.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── CTA ──────────────────────────── %>
<div class="home-cta ctx-black">
  <div class="container-wide" style="padding-top: 5rem; padding-bottom: 5rem; text-align: center;">
    <div style="max-width: 36rem; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p class="heading-1" style="color: white;">Ready to Move?</p>
      <p style="color: var(--color-steel); margin-top: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
        Schedule a call to discuss your deal. No obligation,
        no runaround, just a straight conversation about what is possible.
      </p>
      <div class="home-cta-buttons">
        <%= btn_tag "Schedule a Call", "https://calendly.com/anthony-socalkeys" %>
        <%= btn_tag "Contact Us", "mailto:anthony@linchpinrealty.com" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── FOOTER ──────────────────────────── %>
<footer class="home-footer">
  <div class="home-footer-inner">
    <div>
      <p class="home-footer-brand">Linchpin Realty</p>
      <p class="home-footer-legal">DRE #02018158 &middot; NMLS #2643847</p>
      <p class="home-footer-legal">&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> Linchpin Realty LLC | All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-footer-links">
      <a href="#">About</a>
      <a href="/knowledge">Knowledge</a>
      <a href="#">Contact</a>
      <a href="#">Client Hub</a>
    </div>
    <div class="home-footer-links">
      <a href="mailto:anthony@linchpinrealty.com">Send Us an Email</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
